com.guardianangel.sentiment

Class SentimentClassification

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.guardianangel.sentiment.SentimentClassification

  • public class SentimentClassification
extends Object
    Since:
    1.0.0 Date Created: 11/21/2019 This object is used to store all of the data from the sentiment analysis once it has been complete. Getter methods are called by other classes to use data.
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Christopher DeRoche cderoche@iu.edu
